snippet.title: RAID: Shadow Legends | Couples Therapy | Silent Treatment (Official Commercial)
snippet.description:
As your roster grows and the challenges you face become ever more dangerous, you’ll have to choose the best Champion for every task. Sometimes, it means leaving weaker Champions behind.

They’ve got some opinions on that. It’s that buzzing in your ear.

Don’t take it too hard; you’ve got dozens of bosses and dungeon battles to fight. Tactics and strategies don’t develop themselves. So get out there, gather your forces, and bring the fight to Siroth!

And maybe get some earplugs.

Play RAID: Shadow Legends for free on all devices:
